data.title: The Muralists Beautiful Pain making its film debut August 11th 2023 at the newly renovated Presidio Theatre. I'll be selling tickets soon...
data.meta_description: 195 likes, 11 comments - francolafresh on May 27, 2023: "The Muralists Beautiful Pain making its film debut August 11th 2023 at the newly renovated Presidio Theatre. I'll be selling tickets soon or you can buy at the theatre box office. We will be showing at later dates at the Roxie Theater in San Francisco then in the South Bay at the Plaza De la Raza in San Jose later this year. I'll keep you posted.".
